{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_01_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 1話 大きな仕事",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あふ～っ……私だけ呼び出しって\nいったいなんのご用ですかぁ～～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*yawn* Why are you calling me out\nall alone like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日はライブでしたから、今日はリズノワは\n全員お休みのはず……ふぁ～～っ……すや～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We had a live yesterday‚ so all the members of LizNoir\nare meant to have the day off… *yawn* Zzz….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、疲れてるのは分かるけど起きてくれないか？\nこころに大事な話があるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you’re tired‚ but try to keep your eyes open.\nI’ve something big to share with you‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ん～～むにゃむにゃ……莉央さん、もうパンケーキは\n食べられないですよぉ～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Rio-san‚ no more pancakes…\nI couldn’t possibly… eat any more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "熟睡しないでくれ。それと夢まで見ないでくれ\nこころに仕事のオファーが来てるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop sleeping. And stop dreaming too!\nI’ve got a big job offer for you‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぁっ、お仕事ですか？\nだったら、メンバー全員呼ばないと――はっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*yawn* A new job?\nThen we really do need to call everyone—hold on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "こころと二人きりになって\n今から何をするつもりですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did you ask me to come here alone?\nWhat are you planning on doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "アレですか？　よくあるマネージャーが\nアイドルにやるヤツですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this what I think it is? That managers\ndo to so many idols?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "仕事がほしいなら……分かってるね？　こころ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“If you want the job—you know what to do‚ Kokoro.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ、そんな\n{user}さん信じてたのに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ what a shame!\nI trusted you‚ {user}-san! I really did!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "いくら、こころが星見プロで一番可愛いからって……\nそんなエッチなこと、ファンが許しませんよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know I’m the cutest Hoshimi Productions has…\nbut the fans won’t tolerate such naughty behavior!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのは、こころはNGですから\n悪徳マネージャーにはお仕置きが必要ですね～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a big no no from Kokoro.\nI think you might need to be punished‚ Manager~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いやいやいや\nそんなつもりは微塵もないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ and no again.\nThis isn’t anything like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "ホントですか～～？　でもこころは一番可愛いから\nつい魔が差したり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure? But Kokoro really is the cutest.\nYou’ve fallen for my allure‚ haven’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺は事務所の子は全員、同じくらい魅力的だと思ってる\n誰が一番とか、そういう気持ちはないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I find everyone in the agency equally beautiful.\nI don’t think in terms of who’s the cutest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "え～～っ！？　そういう父親目線ではなく\n異性としてはタイプとかあるんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh? You sound like our father!\nAs a guy‚ you must have a type.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "誰がタイプなんですか？\nあっ、もしかして年齢の近い莉央さんとか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So who’s your type?\nOh‚ maybe Rio-san. You’re closer to her age.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "雑談はこのあたりにして、そろそろ仕事の話をしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Enough joking around. We’ve got work to discuss.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "ちぇっ、{user}さんはノリが悪いですね～\nつまんないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bah. Your reaction is not interesting… {user}-san.\nSo boring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こころ単独でグラビアの話が来てるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve got a request for a solo gravure shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "ノリの悪いマネージャーって、こころは芸能関係者\nとしてどうかと思うんですけ――って、グラビアっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As someone who works in the entertainment industry‚\nmaybe learn to appreciate a joke—hold on! Gravure?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、グラビア。青年誌のヤングミリオン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. gravure. For the magazine Young Million.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "超有名な雑誌じゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s super famous!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "――のウェブ版の特集記事",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a special for their online edition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "え～っ、ウェブ版ですか～？\nてっきり、本誌の表紙も私かと思ったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~! Just the digital one?\nI thought I’d be on the cover and everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、ウェブ版でも凄いことだよ\n大抜擢と言っていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ the digital one is nothing to sniff at.\nThis is a big step up for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "以前、そこの編集長と知り合いになったんだ\nそしたら、昨日話が来て――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been friends with the editor there for a while now.\nHe reached out to me yesterday—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ、ちゃんと仕事してますね\nこころは初めから出来る人だと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ so you do actually do some work around here.\nKokoro knew you were a capable person. I always said it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、髪にホコリが。よろしかったらお肩でも\nお揉みしましょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ there’s a speck of dust in your hair…Shall I give you\na shoulder rub? Would you like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "さっきと態度が180度違うな……\nまあ、その腹黒キャラも君の魅力か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your attitude just did a swift 180‚ huh.\nI guess this scheming character is part of your appeal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "腹黒だなんて、ひどいですよ～。こころは\n臨機応変に強いモノにすり寄ってるだけですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Scheming‚ you say? That’s kinda mean.\nI can respond flexibly to circumstances. Let’s say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.20000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "分かった分かった。で、この話どうする？\n再来週が撮影で時間はあんまりないんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine‚ fine. So what do you say about the job?\nThe shoot is the week after next. We don’t have time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん大丈夫ですよ\nライブの直後で、体も引き締まってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll do it‚ of course.\nIt’s right after the next live‚ so I’ll be in best form.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "ビキニでも、レオタードでも\n可憐に着こなしてみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Put me in a bikini‚ a leotard‚ whatever you need.\nI’ll be cute as can be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "衣装はステージ衣装だよ\nあくまでもパフォーマーとしての特集だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll be wearing your stage outfit.\nThis is a special about you as a performer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんそっち系でも、こころのアイドルスマイルで\n読者のハートをがっちりわしづかみします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can do that too! My idol smile\nwill capture the hearts of all their readers in a vice grip!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。じゃあ、先方には返事を出しておく\nお疲れ様、もう今日は帰ってもいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good. I’ll let them know we’re going ahead.\nWe’re done for today‚ then. You can go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "何を言ってるんですか、{user}さん\n今からすぐに特訓ですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about‚ {user}-san?\nI need to start training now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "今よりさらに、こころの魅力をアップさせるための\nポージングを学びたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to boost my appeal ten-fold for this job!\nPoses. I need to learn more poses!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr026.m4a",
      "text": "だから今すぐこころにコーチをつけて\nレッスンを組んでくれませんか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can you find me a coach?\nPut a lesson plan together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "え？\nでも、さすがに今日からという訳には――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nI think it’s a bit late today to start—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr027.m4a",
      "text": "でもチャンスは最大限に活かさないと\nもったいないですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to maximize this opportunity!\nIt’ll be a shame to let it go to waste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr028.m4a",
      "text": "そこは、{user}さんの\n権力で一つ、お願いしますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ {user}-san.\nSwing some of that manager authority around for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr029.m4a",
      "text": "やるからには、完璧を目指さないと～\n全てのグラドルを過去のものにしてみせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’m going to do this‚ I need to do it perfectly!\nI’ll make all other idol gravure a thing of the past!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "…………不安だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m worried now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.2,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
